title._content: 150 Court Street in Keene New Hampshire

description._content: TITLE 150 Court Street in Keene New Hampshire CREATOR Wardwell, Anne, Keene NH SUBJECT Houses - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION "Also an example of the Queen Ann style, whose characteristics were described earlier, this is one of the best examples of the informal, but well-planned plantings of the late picturesque style of landscaping. As with so many properties in Keene, the original stable constructed in the same style as the house has been retained."
